OL,3,CTrio sentenced for helping teenagers
OL,4,Cwho killed Bristol schoolboys
OL,6,FThree people have been sentenced for
OL,7,Fhelping the teenage killers of Max
OL,8,FDixon and Mason Wrist in the aftermath
OL,9,Fof their murders in Bristol.
OL,11,FDominic Smith, 26, and Marcus
OL,12,FWilliams, 32, were both jailed for
OL,13,Ffour years at Bristol Crown Court.
OL,14,FThey had denied the charge of
OL,15,Fassisting an offender but were
OL,16,Fconvicted at a trial in December,
OL,17,Falong with Ellie-Mae Maddocks.
OL,19,FMs Maddocks, 26, was handed a
OL,20,Fsuspended sentence of two years and
OL,21,F120 hours of unpaid work.
