OL,3,CTrio sentenced for helping teenagers
OL,4,Cwho killed Bristol schoolboys
OL,6,FIt was a case of mistaken identity
OL,7,Fafter the gang wrongly believed the
OL,8,Fpair were responsible for throwing
OL,9,Fbricks at a house in Hartcliffe
OL,10,Fearlier in the evening.
OL,12,FAnthony Snook, Riley Tolliver,
OL,13,FKodishai Wescott and two teenagers,
OL,14,Fwho cannot be named because of their
OL,15,Fyoung age, were found guilty at a
OL,16,Ftrial in 2024 and sentenced to life in
OL,17,Fprison.
