OL,6,FIn the aftermath of the stabbings,
OL,7,FMaddocks and Smith helped Westcott and
OL,8,Fone of the other murderers by letting
OL,9,Fthem stay at their address in Westbury-
OL,10,Fon-Trym overnight. They then drove the
OL,11,Fkillers out of Bristol to further hide
OL,12,Fthem from police.
OL,14,FTolliver arranged for Williams to
OL,15,Fdrive her son, Riley Tolliver, out of
OL,16,FBristol to escape the police and stay
OL,17,Fat his grandmother's in Weston-super-
OL,18,FMare.
