OL,6,F'They delayed justice and did not
OL,7,Fconsider the suffering inflicted on
OL,8,Four family'
OL,10,FMason's mum Nikki Knight had her
OL,11,Fvictim impact statement read out in
OL,12,Fcourt where she wrote: "They made a
OL,13,Fchoice to protect their own and deny
OL,14,Feverything and fight for every step of
OL,15,Fjustice.
OL,17,F"They did not once consider the
OL,18,Fsuffering they inflicted on our
OL,19,Ffamily. They delayed justice. As a
OL,20,Fmother I cannot understand how adults
OL,21,Fcould act with such coldness."
