OL,6,FMax's mum Leanne Ekland said: "We have
OL,7,Fnot been able to grieve Max properly
OL,8,Fas I've been waiting for this trial.
OL,10,F"It doesn't bring Max back. Max and
OL,11,FMason made a choice to go out and get
OL,12,Ffood. They were two innocent boys.
OL,14,F"They were not postcodes. Neither boy
OL,15,Fknew any of the boys. They must have
OL,16,Fbeen terrified. The only comfort I
OL,17,Ftake is that they were together."
