OL,6,FPassing sentence, Judge Peter Blair KC
OL,7,Fwarned that a "line must be drawn"
OL,8,Ffollowing the sentence today.
OL,10,F"Some families in Hartcliffe and
OL,11,FKnowle West have for generations
OL,12,Fperpetrated violent hostility and
OL,13,Frevenge against each other and it must
OL,14,Fbe called out by every parent and
OL,15,Fgrandparent. It must be stopped", he
OL,16,Ftold the courtroom.
OL,18,FHe added: "These two communities will
OL,19,Fspiral downwards into self-destructive
OL,20,Fmadness if not."
